<title>UK: Macro 4 full-year profit rises 4.7 percent.</title>
<headline>Macro 4 full-year profit rises 4.7 percent.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-09-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year to June 30</p>
<p>			   (million stg unless stated)</p>
<p> Shr (pence)		37.5		   vs 35.2</p>
<p> Dividend (pence)	 9.3		    vs 8.6</p>
<p> Total dividend (pence) 24.3		   vs 22.0</p>
<p> Pretax		     12.15		  vs 11.60</p>
<p> Turnover		   25.32		  vs 25.04</p>
<p> Operating result	 11.11		  vs 10.42</p>
<p> Tax			  4.19		   vs 3.83</p>
<p> Pay date		   Nov 4</p>
<p> Div registration date  Sept 17</p>
<p> Ex-div date		Sept 9</p>
<p>NOTE - Macro 4 Plc is a computer sofware maker. The firm expects further growth in earnings per share, but adds that the outcome of rapid changes within the traditional mainframe market is uncertain.</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 7717</p>
